author: jleroux
msg: A patch from Michael Brohl "return value of currentDelegatorTenantId.trim() ignored in org.ofbiz.webapp.control.LoginWorker.login()" https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OFBIZ-
The return value of currentDelegatorTenantId.trim() is not assigned in org.ofbiz.webapp.control.LoginWorker.login() so trim() has no effect.
